backtest: 8 fixtures replayed

sandwich: frontrun-victim-backrun bracket on a WETH/TKN pool
  caught      block 100 sandwich Sandwich
arb: two-hop closed-cycle WETH -> USDC -> WETH
  caught      block 200 arb Arbitrage
flashloan: 100 WETH borrowed and repaid with a fee in one tx
  caught      block 300 flashloan Flashloan
liquidation: 8% bonus seizure of WETH collateral for USDC debt
  caught      block 400 liquidation Liquidation
rugpull: 90% of a pool's TKN reserve drained in one tx
  caught      block 500 rugpull Rugpull
wash-trading: buy/sell/buy/sell round trip on one pool over 4 blocks
  caught      block 603 wash-trading WashTrading
address-poisoning: zero-value bait from an 8-nibble lookalike
  caught      block 700 address-poisoning AddressPoisoning
clean: one ordinary swap and one plain transfer, no incident

per-detector precision / recall:
  address-poisoning    precision 1.000  recall 1.000  (tp=1 fp=0 fn=0)
  arb                  precision 1.000  recall 1.000  (tp=1 fp=0 fn=0)
  flashloan            precision 1.000  recall 1.000  (tp=1 fp=0 fn=0)
  liquidation          precision 1.000  recall 1.000  (tp=1 fp=0 fn=0)
  rugpull              precision 1.000  recall 1.000  (tp=1 fp=0 fn=0)
  sandwich             precision 1.000  recall 1.000  (tp=1 fp=0 fn=0)
  wash-trading         precision 1.000  recall 1.000  (tp=1 fp=0 fn=0)
